== Prerequisites ==
* root user priviledges (either login as root, su -l, or sudo -s)
* mmcblk0p1 is mounted (FAT32) to $MMCFAT
** export MMCFAT="/path/to/fat-mountpoint", ex. /mnt/mmc/1
* mmcblk0p2 is mounted (ext3) to $MMCEXT
** export MMCEXT="/path/to/ext-mountpoint", ex. /mnt/mmc/2

== Download Squashfs Image ==
Go to [[:Category:Image|pre-built images]] and download a <u>.squashfs</u> image.

== AI Touchbook ==

=== Install Image ===

==== Linux Workstation ====
Mount mmcblk0p1
{{Command|mount -t vfat /dev/mmcblk0p1 $MMCFAT}}
Mount mmcblk0p2 and copy squashfs image as root.
{{Command|mount -t ext3 /dev/mmcblk0p2 $MMCEXT}}
{{Command|cp neuvoo-<version>.squashfs $MMCEXT/.images/neuvoo.squashfs}}

== Configure Image ==
Make overlay directory
{{Command|mkdir -p $MMCEXT/.overlay-neuvoo}}

Copy necessary files
{{Command|tar --numeric-owner -xvjpf $MMCFAT/ai-install.tbz2 --wildcards -C $MMCEXT/.overlay-neuvoo ./dev/*}}
{{Command|tar --numeric-owner -xvjpf $MMCFAT/ai-install.tbz2 --wildcards -C $MMCEXT/.overlay-neuvoo ./lib/modules/*}}
{{Command|tar --numeric-owner -xvjpf $MMCFAT/ai-install.tbz2 --wildcards -C $MMCEXT/.overlay-neuvoo ./etc/Wireless/*}}
